WEBVTT

00:00:00.855 --> 00:00:05.489
eydes zogn fun Mala Goldbaum film numer zeks.

00:00:06.205 --> 00:00:13.168
dertseylt mir, ven di krig hot zikh geendikt, vos hot men gezen in Pariz?

00:00:13.663 --> 00:00:18.685
m'hot gezen azoy. di shikses vos hobn gelebt mit di doytshn

00:00:18.709 --> 00:00:24.153
hot men zey opgegolt di hor un naketikerheyt gefirt iber di gasn.

00:00:24.919 --> 00:00:28.051
vayzn zey hobn nisht gedorfn dos tun.

00:00:28.463 --> 00:00:34.026
s'geven a man mit a a a froy iz geblibn, der man iz geven PRISONNIER.

00:00:34.437 --> 00:00:39.139
hot zi zikh arayngenumen a yeke, zi iz geshlofn mit im. er iz ongekumen.

00:00:39.870 --> 00:00:49.348
hot zi gegebn a geshrey, "Frits!" hot er zi geshosn. ven zi shrayt, oy mayn man! volt er zi nisht geshosn.

00:00:49.810 --> 00:00:52.051
hot er volt er im geshosn.

00:00:52.051 --> 00:01:00.283
azoy hot er beyde geshosn, un er hot avekgegebn dem politsey dem revolver un er hot fartseylt far vos, hot men gornisht im getun.

00:01:00.357 --> 00:01:07.202
s'geven a freyd in shtot, a freyd in shtot, s'geven oysergeveyntlekh.

00:01:07.225 --> 00:01:14.323
di frantsoyzn zenen geven gut, "⟨MALHEUR! MALHEUR! MALHEUR!⟩" hobn zey geshr- a rakhmones, a rakhmones oyf zey.

00:01:14.397 --> 00:01:19.500
ober geholfn hobn zey gornisht. gornisht gornisht gornisht gornisht gornisht keyn geholfn.

00:01:20.404 --> 00:01:25.325
vos hobn gezogt ayere kinder ven der krig hot zikh geendikt?

00:01:25.028 --> 00:01:31.316
zey hobn zikh gefreyt. zey hobn zikh gefreyt mit mir! zey hobn mikh derkent!

00:01:31.660 --> 00:01:33.814
di simkhe iz geven groys!

00:01:34.191 --> 00:01:38.775
ikh hob nisht gevust fun fun a tog fun di mames.

00:01:39.118 --> 00:01:45.001
ikh hob nisht gevust fun keyn CUMPLEAMOS, ikh hob nisht gev- m'hot ni- in in Poyln hot men dos nisht gemakht.

00:01:45.666 --> 00:01:50.683
d- in Frankraykh makht men yo, a tog fun di mames, a tog fun di bobes.

00:01:50.683 --> 00:01:55.920
Frankraykh far do bobes oykhet. un a CUMPLEAMOS.

00:01:55.926 --> 00:02:03.462
ikh hob nisht gevust. iz punkt geven a CUMPLEAMOS fun Leonen. AUGOSTA.

00:02:04.836 --> 00:02:14.397
zogt er m- zogt mayn kind azoy. mama, er hot zayn yor, lomir nim epes koyfn. C'EST CUMPLEAMOS.

00:02:14.455 --> 00:02:17.469
zog ikh vos iz di CUMPLEAMOS? vos iz es?

00:02:17.779 --> 00:02:22.143
s'iz C- CUMPLEAMOS dos kind iz geboyrn gevorn dem tog iz CUMPLEAMOS.

00:02:22.605 --> 00:02:25.349
zog ikh im, vos darf men im gebn?

00:02:25.710 --> 00:02:30.328
vet men muzn koyfn a sheyne zakh, a por shikh, a a a antsug, a vos?

00:02:31.363 --> 00:02:33.517
zog ikh e'mir koyfn a por shikhelekh.

00:02:33.895 --> 00:02:38.124
hob ikh im gekoy- hob ikh gevust a tog fun di ge- CUMPLEAMOS.

00:02:38.400 --> 00:02:40.588
s'geven a tog fun di mames.

00:02:42.315 --> 00:02:46.527
ikh halt dos kind oyf der hant, dray-yerike kind oyf der hant,

00:02:47.192 --> 00:02:52.265
un zey poren zikh iber mir, poren zikh iber mir, un tun mir on a por oyringlekh.

00:02:54.043 --> 00:02:56.332
zog ikh, far vos iz dos azoy?

00:02:56.524 --> 00:03:02.542
"haynt iz a tog fun dir, mama! haynt darfstu nisht kokhn un UNK, nor mir gebn dir tsu esn."

00:03:03.223 --> 00:03:05.996
zog ikh, un ver vet kokhn? ver vet gebn tsu esn?

00:03:05.996 --> 00:03:09.849
"mama, eyn tog kum mit undz in in restoran."

00:03:10.783 --> 00:03:14.945
ikh hob tsulib getun. ikh hob zey zeyer lib, ikh hob zeyer lib di kinder.

00:03:15.087 --> 00:03:17.460
ikh bin aropgeganen, m'hot gegesn.

00:03:17.668 --> 00:03:25.661
haynt iz a tog fun di mames, un hot men mir gebrengt a kleydl. on arbl, on arbl, a fartekh.

00:03:26.359 --> 00:03:28.226
zol zayn a fartekh.

00:03:28.620 --> 00:03:32.329
"mama mest dos on tsi s'gut oyf dir, az nisht vel ikh es toyshn."

00:03:32.329 --> 00:03:38.131
hob ikh es ongemostn, s'gut gevezn. darf tsu zayn lenger, vayl m'vasht es oys iz es kertser.

00:03:38.965 --> 00:03:44.488
ikh zog aykh, un zey hobn mir gezogt altsding, ikh hob nisht gevust. nokh dem nokh di krig

00:03:44.488 --> 00:03:48.578
hob ikh gevust altsding shoyn. dos iz dokh geven der frayd.

00:03:50.929 --> 00:03:53.319
ir zent geforn keyn Bolivye?

00:03:53.022 --> 00:03:53.843
yo.

00:03:53.494 --> 00:03:54.318
yo?

00:03:54.253 --> 00:03:55.209
yo.

00:03:54.318 --> 00:03:55.159
Ven?

00:03:56.008 --> 00:04:06.363
ven ikh bin geforn? in zibn un draysikstn, in zibn un fertsikst- zibn un fertsikstn yor, ikh bin bafrayt gevorn fir un fertsik.

00:04:06.370 --> 00:04:10.852
zibn un fertsik. dos ikh gedenk dos yo.

00:04:10.943 --> 00:04:13.536
di kinder zenen oykhet geforn?

00:04:12.765 --> 00:04:15.290
y- on di kinder volt ikh geforn?!

00:04:15.820 --> 00:04:18.497
vu nokh bin ikh geforn? vel ikh ir zogn.

00:04:18.839 --> 00:04:26.242
ikh hob a raykher feter in Amerike. a raykher feter. Maks Goldbaum. a raykher feter.

00:04:27.042 --> 00:04:33.094
hob ikh im geshribn a briv, ikh bin geblibn mit finef kinder un m'hot Yoynem umgebrengt,

00:04:33.319 --> 00:04:35.945
un ikh hob nisht far di kinder gornisht,

00:04:36.103 --> 00:04:39.303
hot er mir geshikt draysik dolar, hob ikh zey tsurikgeshikt.

00:04:40.643 --> 00:04:47.094
draysik dolar, vos hob ikh far draysik dolar, UNK gornisht. na dir tsurik di draysik dolar.

00:04:47.094 --> 00:04:48.993
nor vos hob ikh im getun?

00:04:48.993 --> 00:04:54.592
az ikh hob bedorfn forn keyn Bolivye, bin ikh gekumen in Zhoynt arayn, hobn zey mikh gefregt,

00:04:55.138 --> 00:04:59.266
"host keynemen nisht in Amerike, in an ander land?"

00:04:59.593 --> 00:05:06.691
zog ikh, hob ikh zey gezogt di vorheyt. ikh hob a raykhn feter in Amerike, ober nisht mayner, mayn v- mayn man.

00:05:07.086 --> 00:05:11.146
ober a feter iz er. un er vil mikh nisht anderkenen.

00:05:11.575 --> 00:05:15.602
zeyer a raykher. zogn zey, vu voynt er? in Nyu York.

00:05:16.384 --> 00:05:21.120
vu veys ikh nisht, nor in Nyu York. un er heyst Maks Goldbaum.

00:05:21.514 --> 00:05:28.241
der Leon Fridman hot shoyn im gehat opgezukht. arayn dortn Amerike in Dzhoynt arayn.

00:05:28.804 --> 00:05:31.383
un do hot men im o- oykh gezukht,

00:05:31.383 --> 00:05:38.112
hot er geshikt gelt vifl zey hobn gefodert. far far dray, fir mentshn gelt hobn zey geshikt.

00:05:38.473 --> 00:05:41.927
er hot gehat, er hot er hot. ikh veys nisht tsi er lebt nokh.

00:05:42.557 --> 00:05:47.782
vi azoy zayt ir geforn keyn Bolivye? mit a shif?

00:05:46.742 --> 00:05:48.963
mit di ban, mit in shif.

00:05:48.885 --> 00:05:52.338
ir gedenkt dem nomen fun der shif?

00:05:49.459 --> 00:05:57.130
di shif hot geheysn, gedenk ikh nisht. gedenk ikh oykh nisht.

00:05:57.998 --> 00:06:00.607
vi lang zent ir geblibn in Bolivye?

00:06:01.052 --> 00:06:07.560
in Bolivye bin ikh gevezn un dray kinder hob ikh avekgegebn do aher.

00:06:06.334 --> 00:06:07.577
vi azoy?

00:06:07.633 --> 00:06:09.922
ikh bin aroyfgeganen tsum konsul,

00:06:10.350 --> 00:06:15.755
un di kinder oykhet, hobn zey ongehoybn tsu veynen, zenen krank, zey konen nisht farnemen di luft,

00:06:15.755 --> 00:06:22.191
un viln nisht esn dos esn, vayle di l- zey esn UNK di layzn esn zey oyf.

00:06:22.956 --> 00:06:25.228
dos ershte mol vos ikh hob gezen.

00:06:25.977 --> 00:06:33.092
hot er gehat a rakhmo- ikh hob oykh geveynt far UNK, un vern krank, zey ebn shtarbn do.

00:06:33.756 --> 00:06:41.124
un ikh bin nokh a krig, un er iz dokh antlofn fun Doytshland. fun fun Frankraykh.

00:06:41.316 --> 00:06:44.584
az di doytshn zenen arayn, zenen er iz dokh oykh antlofn.

00:06:44.708 --> 00:06:45.832
ver?

00:06:44.809 --> 00:06:48.043
der konsul is oykhet antlofn.

00:06:49.336 --> 00:06:55.468
hot er gehat rakhmones oyf mir, er hot mir gegebn a PASSAFE, nisht PASSAKHE, a bilete,

00:06:55.525 --> 00:06:59.484
az ikh zol konen araynkumen keyn keyn do aher.

00:07:00.047 --> 00:07:04.845
bin ikh do aher ge- oyf di ban. fir tog un fir nakht ze'mir geforn.

00:07:04.845 --> 00:07:08.701
di Zhak iz shir geshtorbn dort. er hot nisht gehat keyn trunk.

00:07:08.603 --> 00:07:13.187
mit ale finef kinder zent ets geforn? far vos?

00:07:08.701 --> 00:07:13.198
neyn, mit dray, mit dray.

00:07:13.198 --> 00:07:16.494
far di tsvey groyse hob ikh gevolt haltn bay mir.

00:07:17.023 --> 00:07:19.683
vi es makht zikh b- bin ikh mit di kinder.

00:07:20.685 --> 00:07:23.238
dray kinder, arayngegebn keyn MOSAKO.

00:07:23.238 --> 00:07:26.754
donershtik bin ikh gekumen, fraytik hot men zey arayngegebn.

00:07:27.705 --> 00:07:32.221
hob ikh geveynt un geklogt, m'hot mir tsugenumen di kinder, ver veyst nisht tsu doytshn?

00:07:32.937 --> 00:07:36.711
hobn zey gezogt, ruinkt aykh madam, SIGNORA,

00:07:36.987 --> 00:07:45.607
ayere kinder zenen in gute hent, dortn lernt men zingen, m'lernt zey shpiln, m'lernt zey alding oys. zolt ir visn.

00:07:45.607 --> 00:07:50.717
far vos hot men nisht mikh mitgenumen fraytik mit di kinder, ikh zol UNK kumen zuntik?

00:07:52.123 --> 00:07:56.454
hobn dokh gekont mitnemen, ikh zol zen vu di kinder geyn arayn.

00:07:57.102 --> 00:08:01.162
m'hot nisht geha- -kont. s'geforn a COACH aleynt.

00:08:01.472 --> 00:08:06.815
iz geforn tsvey un dray UNK untn nisht geven keyn ort. shoyn.

00:08:07.615 --> 00:08:13.971
mikh hot men arayngegebn Tsyalmento tsvey toyznt nayn, a hotel UNK, s'geven a hotel.

00:08:14.179 --> 00:08:20.112
UNK vi gedenk, hot men mikh dortn arayngegebn, a monat tsayt bin ikh gevezn on gelt.

00:08:20.271 --> 00:08:23.707
esn oykh. esn hob ikh gegesn Nusemkhokhe.

00:08:23.528 --> 00:08:26.256
di tsvey groyse vu zenen zey geven?

00:08:26.683 --> 00:08:29.934
un di tsvey groyse, vu zenen zey gev-

00:08:28.675 --> 00:08:29.951
in Bolivye.

00:08:30.075 --> 00:08:31.689
bay vemen?

00:08:30.582 --> 00:08:32.924
in shtub. in shtub.

00:08:32.924 --> 00:08:36.042
nor hot zey geharget. hot zey geharget.

00:08:36.082 --> 00:08:38.421
ikh bin gekumen hobn zey geveynt far mir.

00:08:38.547 --> 00:08:43.401
er iz nisht geven, hobn zey azoy geveynt, "mame, hot zi undz shir derharget!"

00:08:43.356 --> 00:08:44.413
der man?

00:08:44.233 --> 00:08:47.585
yo, a man, a shpa- a shpanyer iz er geven.

00:08:47.794 --> 00:08:53.002
zog ikh, kinderlekh, ikh voyn nisht mit im. far keyn shum gelt nisht.

00:08:54.477 --> 00:08:58.706
dos meydl hot zikh bakent mit dem yingl, dem eydem.

00:08:59.202 --> 00:09:03.071
hot zi g- hot zi gevolt, m'hot ir geredt a raykhn shidekh,

00:09:03.071 --> 00:09:06.957
zogt zi, mam- mama, a raykhn shidekh vil ikh nisht.

00:09:07.116 --> 00:09:10.023
vet er shtendik zogn ikh bin an orem meydl geven.

00:09:10.023 --> 00:09:14.906
ikh nem an orem yingl, kon er nisht zogn az ikh bin an oreme, iz er oykh a oremer.

00:09:15.081 --> 00:09:19.733
hot zikh bakent mit dem yingl. mama, makht zi, s'gefelt mir Mark.

00:09:21.088 --> 00:09:27.748
zog ikh, her oys, dos beste yingl fun Bolivye iz Mark. a shtiler, a voyler.

00:09:28.210 --> 00:09:32.034
nor der foter hot zikh derredt, er iz gekumen mit a foter.

00:09:33.053 --> 00:09:38.329
un un ikh hob im gegebn a vayb, hot er khasene gehat. ikh hob im gegebn a vayb.

00:09:39.162 --> 00:09:48.588
zog ikh, ikh eb beser tun. ikh eb arayngeyn tsu Salin, ikh eb bald visn tsi der foter vet veln.

00:09:49.101 --> 00:09:54.545
ikh bin arayngeganen tsu der froy Sali un zi hot mikh zeyer ge- zeyer gintsik geyn.

00:09:54.552 --> 00:10:00.199
zog ikh, froy Sale, veyst gants gut s'iz a yesoyme.

00:10:00.880 --> 00:10:08.146
khasene hobn darf zi nisht, zi iz alt akhtsn yor. darf zi nisht. zi iz nokh yung.

00:10:08.203 --> 00:10:19.996
ober z- vil er khasene mit Markn. di gantse shtot veyst az zi geyt mit Mark, Mark iz ir khosn. zolt ir visn. vos tut men?

00:10:19.996 --> 00:10:24.583
zogt zi, vi eyder an ander meydl er zol nemen zol er nemen Suzan.

00:10:24.623 --> 00:10:29.814
zol er nemen ayer Suzan. azoy er iz, er iz orem, zi iz orem. zoln zey khasene hobn.

00:10:29.500 --> 00:10:31.350
ver iz geven di froy?

00:10:31.255 --> 00:10:33.318
?

00:10:31.643 --> 00:10:33.341
ver iz zi geven?

00:10:33.318 --> 00:10:37.644
di froy iz oykh geven a gelitene. oykh gekumen mit a kind.

00:10:38.089 --> 00:10:45.339
hot zi khasene gehat mit zayn foter. un zi hot mikh tsugeholfn. zey hobn khasene gehat.

00:10:45.447 --> 00:10:51.518
az zey hobn kha- un dos yingl iz antlofn, ven ikh bin gekumen fun b- fun danet, iz er antlofn.

00:10:51.518 --> 00:10:58.114
hot im geharget tsu toyt. hot im geharget. hob ikh im gegebn an adres keyn Khovita.

00:10:54.897 --> 00:10:56.376
ayer zun?

00:10:59.082 --> 00:11:04.630
ikh hob ikh hob opgezukht Khovita. ikh hob im gegebn an an adres, dos iz mayn kuzin.

00:11:04.630 --> 00:11:07.513
hot er ge- arayngegangen tsun im, un er hot gearbet.

00:11:08.363 --> 00:11:14.904
dos yingl hot gehat gut un opgedungen a pensyon un er hot getsolt, di ⟨ARMY⟩ hot getsolt, nisht er.

00:11:15.180 --> 00:11:19.291
shoyn, fun dem fun di dr- fir kinder hob ikh shoyn gehat dr-

00:11:20.040 --> 00:11:27.189
iberlozn a meydl un avekforn hob ikh nisht gevolt. dos meydl iz mayn lebn. mayn lebn mayn gezunt.

00:11:27.769 --> 00:11:30.969
ikh vel zi nisht UNK avekforn biz zi vet khasene hobn.

00:11:31.532 --> 00:11:34.394
un hot khasene gehat bay tsvey un tsvontsik yor.

00:11:35.717 --> 00:11:43.760
un s- ikh hob gezen s'a gut kind un er iz a guter man, hob ikh zi gelozt un ikh bin geforn do aher.

00:11:44.961 --> 00:11:50.476
akht un fertsikstn yor ven Khovita iz geshtorbn bin ikh gekumen do aher.

00:11:51.495 --> 00:11:55.319
bin ikh krank gevezn, s'hot zikh gelozt blut fun mir.

00:11:55.393 --> 00:12:01.580
gezen dos! gezen do! azelkhene khmales blut aroysgeganen.

00:12:01.907 --> 00:12:09.346
iz gekumen a dokter, a terkisher, hot er nor gevolt gelt fun mir, "fuftsik sent, fuftsik sent, fuftsik sent."

00:12:09.346 --> 00:12:14.338
damolts fuftsik sent iz geven gelt, in zibn un fertsikstn yor.

00:12:14.665 --> 00:12:20.683
az ikh bin gekumen in zibn un fertsikstn yor, hob ikh bin ikh gekumen keyn Bolivye.

00:12:21.313 --> 00:12:24.327
in tsvey un fuftsikstn yor bin ikh gekumen.

00:12:25.870 --> 00:12:35.466
un un ikh hob mikh nisht gekont rirn. er hot gezen ikh bin shoyn toyt hot er mikh ge- farviklt in laylekh, er hot mikh gefirt in HOSPITAL Alevyar.

00:12:35.995 --> 00:12:40.157
Alevyar in ershtn in ershtn ODDZIAL. in ershte SALLE.

00:12:41.226 --> 00:12:45.759
o- iz geven der dokter Luti, a doytshisher dokter, a profesor.

00:12:46.103 --> 00:12:50.130
er hot gegebn a kuk on mikh, fun vanet kumt dos?

00:12:50.659 --> 00:12:53.693
vos iz geshen? un do iz geven shvarts.

00:12:53.693 --> 00:12:57.504
hot men gegebn a nodl do arayn. yeke.

00:12:58.050 --> 00:13:08.152
di di do- di di di vi heysn zey di andere zelner? di andere zelner.

00:13:08.344 --> 00:13:12.321
di natsis? di natsis? ver?

00:13:12.377 --> 00:13:17.821
zey zey zey hobn mir gegebn a nodl. fun an andere shtot zenen zey.

00:13:18.250 --> 00:13:19.830
di ukrainer?

00:13:18.739 --> 00:13:23.947
ukrainer, yo, ukrainer.

00:13:21.270 --> 00:13:23.930
far vos hot men aykh gegebn a nodl?

00:13:24.072 --> 00:13:31.046
f- er hot gev- er hot UNK. er hot gevolt zen, az ikh vel im oyszogn vu di kinder zenen.

00:13:31.046 --> 00:13:33.515
un a krenk im hob ikh oysgezogt.

00:13:33.943 --> 00:13:39.607
UNK tu vos du vilst mit mir, makh mir UNK, di kinder gib ikh nisht aroys.

00:13:40.356 --> 00:13:44.990
er hot mir gemakht a nodl, iz gevorn shvarts do, arum un arum shvarts.

00:13:45.638 --> 00:13:48.469
ikh bin gekumen in dem HOSPITAL, dokter Luti,

00:13:48.469 --> 00:13:53.461
"akh got mayn got! akh got mayn got! geb nor a kuk!"

00:13:53.569 --> 00:13:57.022
azoy hot er geshrign. er hot geveynt, er hot geveynt.

00:13:57.501 --> 00:14:03.705
un er hot mikh geratevet, un dokter Kaplan. Salomon Kaplan hot mikh geratevet.

00:14:03.913 --> 00:14:08.582
zey hobn gekont Salomon Kaplan? a guter profesor.

00:14:08.622 --> 00:14:12.412
haynt hobn di kinder, di kinder hobn es.

00:14:12.604 --> 00:14:14.786
zey beyde hobn mikh geratevet.

00:14:14.786 --> 00:14:18.878
ir veyst vos? zey hobn mikh aroysgeshikt oyf a monat tsayt tsu a

00:14:18.878 --> 00:14:24.495
in a kompen- in a k- in a ⟨KONYOYNE⟩, vu m'get tsu esn, s'nisht keyn ge-,

00:14:24.535 --> 00:14:28.443
zey hobn mikh aroysgeshikt. a monat tsayt bin ikh gevezn.

00:14:28.517 --> 00:14:33.624
un di froy hot mikh gehitn vi m'hit an oytser. a voyle froy.

00:14:33.782 --> 00:14:40.036
ikh hob gehat gut. un nisht vayt danet.

00:14:41.072 --> 00:14:45.149
nisht vayt fun danet. azoy gedenk ikh un azoy gedenk ikh nisht.

00:14:43.941 --> 00:14:51.411
zogt mir, vos nokh hot men aykh getun dortn in in kontsentratsye lager vos dernokh hot ir gelitn?

00:14:52.260 --> 00:14:55.173
ir hot gezogt az men hot aykh gegebn a nodl.

00:14:55.905 --> 00:14:59.611
men hot aykh do gegebn a nodl. vos nokh,

00:14:57.205 --> 00:14:58.329
a nodl.

